**who —** SONY PLAYSTATION 2 · PS2 — an exereunesis sphere — the teardown

**what —** The best-selling console ever built its case on two things: a wildly powerful, eccentric custom CPU called the Emotion Engine, and a DVD drive that also made it the cheapest DVD player in the house. Hard to program, backward-compatible with the PS1, and unstoppable in the market.

